<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="諾芙新人畢業紀念周邊抽獎頁面，支援單抽、十連抽、榜單與再來一次計數。">
  <title>諾芙新人畢業紀念周邊抽獎</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="background-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="background-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <main class="page-shell">
    <header class="hero">
      <p class="hero__tag">Nove Graduation Memorial</p>
      <h1>諾芙新人畢業紀念周邊抽獎</h1>
      <p class="hero__description">
        輸入名稱後即可單抽或十連抽。中大獎會自動加入榜單，抽到「再來一次」會累加到右側計數器。
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="dashboard" aria-label="抽獎資訊面板">
      <article class="panel panel--leaderboard">
        <div class="panel__header">
          <h2>大獎榜單</h2>
          <button id="resetLeaderboardButton" class="button button--ghost" type="button">重置榜單</button>
        </div>
        <p class="panel__hint">僅記錄抽中大獎的結果，並會保存在瀏覽器本機。</p>
        <ul id="leaderboardList" class="leaderboard-list"></ul>
        <p id="leaderboardEmpty" class="panel__empty">目前還沒有人抽中大獎。</p>
      </article>

      <article class="panel panel--counter">
        <div class="panel__header">
          <h2>再來一次計數器</h2>
          <button id="resetRetryButton" class="button button--ghost" type="button">清空計數</button>
        </div>
        <p class="retry-counter__value"><span id="retryCount">0</span></p>
        <p class="panel__hint">抽到「再來一次」時會自動累加，重新整理頁面也會保留。</p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="draw-card" aria-label="抽獎操作區">
      <label class="input-group" for="username">
        <span class="input-group__label">參加者名稱</span>
        <input type="text" id="username" maxlength="24" placeholder="請輸入您的名稱" autocomplete="off">
      </label>

      <div class="button-row">
        <button id="drawOnceButton" class="button button--primary" type="button">抽獎一次</button>
        <button id="drawTenButton" class="button button--secondary" type="button">抽獎十次</button>
      </div>

      <section class="probability-card" aria-label="獎項機率">
        <h2>獎項機率</h2>
        <ul id="probabilityList" class="probability-list"></ul>
      </section>

      <section class="results-section" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="false">
        <div class="results-section__header">
          <h2>抽獎結果</h2>
          <button id="clearResultsButton" class="button button--ghost" type="button">清空結果</button>
        </div>
        <div id="resultsContainer" class="results-container"></div>
        <p id="resultsPlaceholder" class="results-placeholder">尚未抽獎，結果會顯示在這裡。</p>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script src="assets/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
